      "text": "目录条目对象（CatalogEntryObject）\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+---------------------+-------------------\n-----------------+\n  | FieldTag=99 (2B)     | CatalogType (1~4B)         | FieldTag=100 (2B)   |\nCreateInfo 负载（变长）             |\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+---------------------+-------------------\n-----------------+\n  |← 类型属性号 →|← 枚举值 →|← 负载属性号 →|\nSchema/Table/View/Sequence/Type/Macro/TableMacro/Index |",
