      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "目录条目对象（CatalogEntryObject）\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+---------------------+------------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=99 (2B)     | CatalogType (1~4B)         | FieldTag=100 (2B)   | CreateInfo 负载（变长）             |\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+---------------------+------------------------------------+\n  |← 类型属性号 →|← 枚举值 →|← 负载属性号 →| Schema/Table/View/Sequence/Type/Macro/TableMacro/Index |",
