      "text": "Table Entry 中的“表级元数据”（SingleFileTableDataWriter::FinalizeTable）\n+----------------------------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------+------------+-------------------------+-------------+--------------------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------+-------------+---------------------------------------------+\n| TableStatistics（变长）| RowGroupCount u64(8B)  | RowGroupPointer[0..M-1]（变长）| 101 (2B) | table_pointer (12B)  | 102 (2B)  | total_rows u64(8B)  |  103 (2B)   | index_pointers 旧版（12B×K，变长）| 104 (2B)  | index_storage_infos 新版（变长×L）  |\n+----------------------------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------+------------+-------------------------+-------------+--------------------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------+-------------+---------------------------------------------+\n|←    列统计单元        →|←       行组数量            →|←         行组指针序列            →|←              表指针              →|←            表的总行数             →|     ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Table Entry 中的“表级元数据”（SingleFileTableDataWriter::FinalizeTable）\n+----------------------------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------+------------+-------------------------+-------------+--------------------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------+-------------+---------------------------------------------+\n| TableStatistics（变长）| RowGroupCount u64(8B)  | RowGroupPointer[0..M-1]（变长）| 101 (2B) | table_pointer (12B)  | 102 (2B)  | total_rows u64(8B)  |  103 (2B)   | index_pointers 旧版（12B×K，变长）| 104 (2B)  | index_storage_infos 新版（变长×L）  |\n+----------------------------+--------------------------------+----------------------------------------+------------+-------------------------+-------------+--------------------------+----------------+-------------------------------------------+-------------+---------------------------------------------+\n|←    列统计单元        →|←       行组数量            →|←         行组指针序列            →|←              表指针              →|←            表的总行数             →|     ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
