      "text": "RowGroupPointer（单独展开 RowGroup::Serialize）\n+-------------+-------------------------+-------------+---------------------------+-------------+------------------------------------------------+---------------+-------------------------------------------------+--------------+---------------------------------+----------------+---------------------------------------------------------+\n| 100 (2B)  | row_start u64(8B)  | 101 (2B)  | tuple_count u64(8B)  | 102 (2B)  | data_pointers: Count u64(8B) + 12B×C |  103 (2B)   | delete_pointers: Count u64(8B) + 12B×C|  104 (2B)  | has_metadata_blocks(1B) |  105 (2B)    | extra_metadata_blocks: Count u64(8B)+8B×C  |\n+-------------+-------------------------+-------------+---------------------------+-------------+------------------------------------------------+---------------+-------------------------------------------------+--------------+---------------------------------+----------------+---------------------------------------------------------+\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "RowGroupPointer（单独展开 RowGroup::Serialize）\n+-------------+-------------------------+-------------+---------------------------+-------------+------------------------------------------------+---------------+-------------------------------------------------+--------------+---------------------------------+----------------+---------------------------------------------------------+\n| 100 (2B)  | row_start u64(8B)  | 101 (2B)  | tuple_count u64(8B)  | 102 (2B)  | data_pointers: Count u64(8B) + 12B×C |  103 (2B)   | delete_pointers: Count u64(8B) + 12B×C|  104 (2B)  | has_metadata_blocks(1B) |  105 (2B)    | extra_metadata_blocks: Count u64(8B)+8B×C  |\n+-------------+-------------------------+-------------+---------------------------+-------------+------------------------------------------------+---------------+-------------------------------------------------+--------------+---------------------------------+----------------+---------------------------------------------------------+\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
