      "text": "  MetaBlockPointer\n  +------------------------+-------------------+\n  | block_id u64(8B)    | offset u32(4B)|\n  +------------------------+-------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  MetaBlockPointer\n  +------------------------+-------------------+\n  | block_id u64(8B)    | offset u32(4B)|\n  +------------------------+-------------------+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8bcu-UfHqkfcKw1halaxB",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4985.3947397867905,
      "y": 693.1119791666664,
      "width": 532.7197875976562,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1512836242,
      "version": 264,
      "versionNonce": 37153938,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772541254152,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "  IndexPointers（旧版列表，单独展开）\n  +------------------------+----------------------------+\n  | Count u64(8B)      | BlockPointer[0..K-1]     |\n  +------------------------+----------------------------+\n  |← 元素个数 →| 每项 12B：block_id(8B)+offset(4B) |",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  IndexPointers（旧版列表，单独展开）\n  +------------------------+----------------------------+\n  | Count u64(8B)      | BlockPointer[0..K-1]     |\n  +------------------------+----------------------------+\n  |← 元素个数 →| 每项 12B：block_id(8B)+offset(4B) |",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "C6Nz7lHPWqeibDmsEQlSQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2767.4121856689517,
      "y": 1263.8020833333328,
      "width": 615,
      "height": 525,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3b",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 111533966,
      "version": 373,
      "versionNonce": 73867278,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772537842359,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "    +================= MetaBlock(root) =================+\n    | Field[100] \"catalog_entries\": List<N>                        |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=SCHEMA,  [100] schema=... }           |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TABLE,   [100] table=...                |\n    |   |    // 紧随其后：TableMetadata 单元                      |\n    |   |    Unit TableStatistics                                     |\n    |   |    u64 row_group_count                                    |\n    |   |    Seq RowGroupPointer[...]                                |\n    |   |    [101] table_pointer                                       |\n    |   |    [102] total_rows                                         |\n    |   |    [103] index_pointers (旧) /                             |\n    |   |    [104] index_storage_infos (新)                        |\n    |   |     }                                                            |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=VIEW,     [100] view=... }               |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=SEQUENCE, [100] sequence=... }      |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TYPE,     [100] type=... }              |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=MACRO,    [100] macro=... }            |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TABLE_MACRO,[100] table_macro...}|\n    |   └─ { [99] type=INDEX,    [100] index=...               |\n    |        [101] root_block_pointer (旧版可选) }                |\n    +===================================================+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "    +================= MetaBlock(root) =================+\n    | Field[100] \"catalog_entries\": List<N>                        |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=SCHEMA,  [100] schema=... }           |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TABLE,   [100] table=...                |\n    |   |    // 紧随其后：TableMetadata 单元                      |\n    |   |    Unit TableStatistics                                     |\n    |   |    u64 row_group_count                                    |\n    |   |    Seq RowGroupPointer[...]                                |\n    |   |    [101] table_pointer                                       |\n    |   |    [102] total_rows                                         |\n    |   |    [103] index_pointers (旧) /                             |\n    |   |    [104] index_storage_infos (新)                        |\n    |   |     }                                                            |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=VIEW,     [100] view=... }               |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=SEQUENCE, [100] sequence=... }      |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TYPE,     [100] type=... }              |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=MACRO,    [100] macro=... }            |\n    |   ├─ { [99] type=TABLE_MACRO,[100] table_macro...}|\n    |   └─ { [99] type=INDEX,    [100] index=...               |\n    |        [101] root_block_pointer (旧版可选) }                |\n    +===================================================+",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8VER9yK_lOmBxd0AUssqo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2787.7311960856214,
      "y": 941.888020833333,
      "width": 770,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
