      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772542206414,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "struct RowGroupPointer {\n        uint64_t row_start;\n        uint64_t tuple_count;\n        //! The data pointers of the column segments stored in the row group\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> data_pointers;\n        //! Data pointers to the delete information of the row group (if any)\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> deletes_pointers;\n        //! Whether or not we have all metadata blocks defined in the pointer\n        bool has_metadata_blocks = false;\n        //! Metadata blocks of the columns that are not mentioned in \"data_pointers\"\n        //! This is often empty - but can be set for wide columns with a lot of metadata\n        vector<idx_t> extra_metadata_blocks;\n};",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "struct RowGroupPointer {\n        uint64_t row_start;\n        uint64_t tuple_count;\n        //! The data pointers of the column segments stored in the row group\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> data_pointers;\n        //! Data pointers to the delete information of the row group (if any)\n        vector<MetaBlockPointer> deletes_pointers;\n        //! Whether or not we have all metadata blocks defined in the pointer\n        bool has_metadata_blocks = false;\n        //! Metadata blocks of the columns that are not mentioned in \"data_pointers\"\n        //! This is often empty - but can be set for wide columns with a lot of metadata\n        vector<idx_t> extra_metadata_blocks;\n};",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hPuTFX86V5SdZfYOKjUvQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5488.489578247081,
      "y": 490.0846354166662,
      "width": 793.07958984375,
      "height": 475,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3r",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 697272914,
      "version": 61,
      "versionNonce": 253705038,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772541336272,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "  1. 表级元数据中的旧版索引列表\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=103 (2B)    | index_pointers 列表        |\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+\n  |← 属性号 →| Count u64(8B) + BlockPointer[0..K-1]   |\n  其中每个 BlockPointer（12B）为：\n  +------------------------+-------------------+\n  | block_id u64(8B)       | offset u32(4B)    |\n  +------------------------+-------------------+\n  2. Catalog 的 INDEX 条目（旧版可带根指针）\n  +----------------------+-----------------------------+------------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=99 (2B)     | CatalogType=INDEX(1~4B) |                            |\n  +----------------------+-----------------------------+------------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=100 (2B)   | CreateIndexInfo（变长 | 索引的建议信息（名称/列/唯一\n性等）   |\n  +----------------------+-----------------------------+------------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=101 (2B)  | root_block_pointer(12B，可选)| BlockPointer（索引根块\n指针）        |\n  +----------------------+-----------------------------+------------------------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "  1. 表级元数据中的旧版索引列表\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=103 (2B)    | index_pointers 列表        |\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+\n  |← 属性号 →| Count u64(8B) + BlockPointer[0..K-1]   |\n  其中每个 BlockPointer（12B）为：\n  +------------------------+-------------------+\n  | block_id u64(8B)       | offset u32(4B)    |\n  +------------------------+-------------------+\n  2. Catalog 的 INDEX 条目（旧版可带根指针）\n  +----------------------+-----------------------------+------------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=99 (2B)     | CatalogType=INDEX(1~4B) |                            |\n  +----------------------+-----------------------------+------------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=100 (2B)   | CreateIndexInfo（变长 | 索引的建议信息（名称/列/唯一性等）   |\n  +----------------------+-----------------------------+------------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=101 (2B)  | root_block_pointer(12B，可选)| BlockPointer（索引根块指针）        |\n  +----------------------+-----------------------------+------------------------------------+",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yRZQDm_pJGIPs45phtZrt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6344.215316772469,
      "y": 509.2643229166664,
      "width": 797.0187377929688,
      "height": 425,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3s",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1483814158,
      "version": 85,
      "versionNonce": 723968974,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772541339194,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "表级元数据中的新版索引存储信息\n  +----------------------+----------------------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=104 (2B)    | index_storage_infos 列表                      |\n  +----------------------+----------------------------------------------+\n  |← 属性号 →| Count u64(8B) + IndexStorageInfo[0..L-1]（变长逐项）       |\n  每个 IndexStorageInfo（示意字段）：\n  +----------------------+------------------------------+-------------------------------------+\n  | name（变长）| allocator_infos 列表（变长）| 其它元数据（类型/参数等）     |\n  +----------------------+---------------------------+--------------------------------------+\n  allocator_infos 的每项包含：\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+\n  | block_pointers 列表   | Count u64(8B) + 12B×M      |\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+\n  其中 12B 的 BlockPointer 同旧版定义：\n  +------------------------+-------------------+\n  | block_id u64(8B)       | offset u32(4B)    |\n  +------------------------+-------------------+",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "表级元数据中的新版索引存储信息\n  +----------------------+----------------------------------------------+\n  | FieldTag=104 (2B)    | index_storage_infos 列表                      |\n  +----------------------+----------------------------------------------+\n  |← 属性号 →| Count u64(8B) + IndexStorageInfo[0..L-1]（变长逐项）       |\n  每个 IndexStorageInfo（示意字段）：\n  +----------------------+------------------------------+-------------------------------------+\n  | name（变长）| allocator_infos 列表（变长）| 其它元数据（类型/参数等）     |\n  +----------------------+---------------------------+--------------------------------------+\n  allocator_infos 的每项包含：\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+\n  | block_pointers 列表   | Count u64(8B) + 12B×M      |\n  +----------------------+----------------------------+\n  其中 12B 的 BlockPointer 同旧版定义：\n  +------------------------+-------------------+\n  | block_id u64(8B)       | offset u32(4B)    |\n  +------------------------+-------------------+",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
